snippet.title: Johnny Depp Sued by His Lawyers | Daily Celebrity News | Splash TV
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp has reportedly been sued by his lawyers for not paying them since July.

SUBSCRIBE NOW : https://goo.gl/JaLP0U

Johnny Depp may have unloaded 5 Los Angeles penthouses, but it sounds like he still has money issues.

Lawyers for the movie star have filed a counter lawsuit against him, insisting that his reputation never suffered due to their services.

In case you didn’t know, Johnny sued execs at a prestigious lawfirm, alleging they mismanaged his finances.

But he learned what happens when you sue lawyers.

They sue you back.

The legal eagles claim they haven’t been paid since July and they can’t be held responsible for his financial problems. 

And if you’ve been following the news, you know Depp has a lot of financial problems.

Somebody better get this guy some acting gigs.
